RESTful Services



		Anyframe supports Web Service using Apache CXF 2.3.0 version, 
		and provides REST architecture style Web Service on HTTP protocol along with SOAP protocol based Web Service. 
		Refer to Anyframe CXF-JAXWS Plugin manual for SOAP protocol based Web Service.


